### Polling App API Requests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### Create a new poll
POST {{baseUrl}}/polls
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Best Programming Language",
  "question": "Which programming language do you prefer?",
  "options": ["Go", "Rust", "Python", "JavaScript"]
}

###

### Create another poll
POST {{baseUrl}}/polls
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Best Go Web Framework",
  "question": "What's your favorite Go web framework?",
  "options": ["Gin", "Echo", "Chi", "Fiber"]
}

###

### List all polls
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls

###

### Get a specific poll (replace 1 with actual poll ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/polls/1

###

### Vote on a poll option (replace 1 with poll ID, option_index with 0-3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/polls/1/vote
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "option_index": 0
}

###

### Vote on another option
POST {{baseUrl}}/polls/1/vote
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "option_index": 2
}

###

### Delete a poll (replace 1 with poll ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/polls/1

###
